title: OXO® Good Grips™ Mango Splitter
description:
One simple press removes the seed and cuts the fruit in half. The splitter's sharp and sturdy serrated blades slice cleanly through the fruit and leave almost nothing behind on the seed. The ergonomic soft grips cushion your hand while you press. 
To purchase this item, please visit: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-1102433/OXO-Good-Grips-Mango-Splitter
